head.title: Welcome to School District of Flambeau

div.p: Effective Tuesday, March 17, 2020 at 4:00 p.m. the School District of Flambeau will be closed UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE. Please watch our Facebook and website pages for any further changes, plus power announcements will be sent out. Updates and information regarding COVID-19 can be found here.
